Package lib.aide.tabular

Record Class TabularRowsRequestForSP.FilterModel

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
lib.aide.tabular.TabularRowsRequestForSP.FilterModel
Record Components:
filterType - The type of the filter (e.g., text, number).
type - The comparison type (e.g., equals, inRange).
filter - The primary filter value.
filterTo - The secondary filter value (e.g., for "between").
operator - Logical operator (AND/OR) for combining conditions.
conditions - Nested conditions for complex filters.
secondFilter - A secondary filter for complex logic.
dateFrom - Starting date for date range filters.
dateTo - Ending date for date range filters.
Enclosing class:
TabularRowsRequestForSP
